her a little bit of iron.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.000
Let's just see if she has,

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:30.910
we measured her ferritin,

00:06:30.910 --> 00:06:33.350
and it turns out that
she has restless legs.

00:06:33.350 --> 00:06:35.340
And the parents said she
got much better quickly

00:06:35.340 --> 00:06:36.230
after we treated her.

00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:39.180
I think we gave her a
low dose of pramipexole,

00:06:39.180 --> 00:06:41.550
which we can talk about
later, a medication.

00:06:41.550 --> 00:06:42.383
But the interesting thing is

00:06:42.383 --> 00:06:43.340
when she learned to speak English,

00:06:43.340 --> 00:06:45.681
