00:06:45.681 --> 00:06:48.610
'Cause she would say "itchy",
she knew what she had.

00:06:48.610 --> 00:06:50.480
So restless legs is
something to think about.

00:06:50.480 --> 00:06:53.490
And when you see it in a kid,
always ask about the parents.

00:06:53.490 --> 00:06:54.890
And you have to always ask that

00:06:54.890 --> 00:06:58.640
