are thanked with gratitude,

00:09:39.380 --> 00:09:41.690
because it helped me think
about how I want to do things,

00:09:41.690 --> 00:09:43.320
and how it goes.

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:44.710
But anyway, that's delayed
sleep phase syndrome.

00:09:44.710 --> 00:09:45.963
So learn that condition.

00:09:48.217 --> 00:09:51.620
"My child won't sleep, my child is tired."

00:09:51.620 --> 00:09:53.070
Wouldn't it be nice if
we could have kids sleep

00:09:53.070 --> 00:09:54.331
whenever we wanted to?

00:09:54.331 --> 00:09:55.272
